							<div class="post_wrapper author">
								<div id="about_the_author">
									<div class="gravatar"><a href="https://lithub.com/author/dwyer-murphy/"><img src="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/dwyer-murphy-100x100.jpg" width="100" height="100" srcset="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/dwyer-murphy-300x300.jpg 2x" alt="Dwyer Murphy" class="avatar avatar-100 wp-user-avatar wp-user-avatar-100 alignnone photo" /></a></div>
									<div class="description author withsidebar">
										<h6><a href="https://lithub.com/author/dwyer-murphy/">Dwyer Murphy</a></h6>
										Dwyer Murphy's new book is The House on Buzzards Bay, available June 24, 2025 from Viking Books. He is the author of An Honest Living and The Stolen Coast, both of which were New York Times Editors’ Choice selections. He is the editor in chief of Literary Hub‘s CrimeReads vertical																			</div>
